fields.summary: DELETE_FAILED stack state reached due to IGW delete failure

comments.body: Re-ran {{euform-delete-stack}}, and the stack deleted successfully.  Looks like this behavior occurred due to heavy swapping on the Eucalyptus (CLC, UFS) components.

The issue couldn't be reproduced on a cloud with sufficient amount of RAM on the CLC and UFS.  Since the cloud that this issue was discovered had signs of heavy swapping, this seems to have contributed to this behavior.  Therefore, closing the ticket.
